==Unicode編碼==
在Unicode標準6.0中為佉盧文分配了範圍U+U+10A00–U+U+10A58。

現在支援這些字元的字體有[[Noto字体|Noto Sans Kharoshthi]]<ref>[https://github.com/googlefonts/noto-fonts/tree/master/phaseIII_only/unhinted/otf/NotoSansKharoshthi Noto Sans Kharoshthi下載頁]</ref>和Windows 10內建的Segoe UI Historic <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/goglobal/bb688099.aspx#W10 |title=MSDN: Script and Font Support in Windows |accessdate=2016-03-23 |archive-date=2016-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408223112/https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/goglobal/bb688099.aspx#W10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

